        threat to the global commitment to mitigate greenhouse gas emissions
        under the Paris Agreement'[64], especially in the context of gloomy
        forecasts stating that 'Bitcoin emissions alone could push global
        warming above 2 C' [65]."</em
      >
    </blockquote>
